<graph edgedefault="undirected"><node id="&quot;IMAGE_16&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORI_IMG"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The image displays a small, low-resolution, black-and-white icon, likely a pictogram. It consists of a prominent white circular shape centered within a black square frame. Inside the white circle, there are two thin, dark vertical shapes. The shape on the left is shorter and has a slightly broader, multi-pronged top, characteristic of a fork. The shape on the right is longer and narrower, with a pointed or rounded top, resembling a knife. These two utensils are positioned side-by-side, suggesting an icon for food service or a restaurant, consistent with the surrounding text mentioning "food service.""</data>
  <data key="d2">C:/MMGraphRAG/MMGraphRAG/test_runs/api_working\images\image_16.jpg</data>
</node>
